Information
===========

This is the PASCAL3D+ benchmark [1] for 3D object detection and pose estimation.
We augments 12 rigid categories of the PASCAL VOC 2012 [2] with 3D annotations.
Furthermore, more images are added to each category from ImageNet [3].
The annotations are in the .mat format of MATLAB.

For questions concerning the benchmark, please contact Yu Xiang at
<yuxiang AT umich DOT edu>.

This project has been supported by ONR grant N00014-13-1-0761 and NFS CAREER
grant #1054127.


References
==========

[1] Y. Xiang, R. Mottaghi, and S. Savarese.
Beyond PASCAL: A benchmark for 3D detection in the Wild. In WACV, 2014.

[2] M. Everingham, L. Van Gool, C. K. I. Williams, J. Winn, and A. Zisserman.
The pascal visual object classes (voc) challenge. IJCV, 2010.

[3] J. Deng, W. Dong, R. Socher, L. Li, K. Li, and L. Fei-Fei.
Imagenet: A large scale hierarchical image database. In CVPR, 2009.


