Basic Usage
===========

There are four directories in this package:

1. Annotations. The augmented PASCAL annotations for the 12 categories.
2. Annotation_tool. The annotation tool for 3D annotation, and some scripts to visualize the annotations.
                    The scripts are helpful to understand the format of the annotation.
3. CAD. The CAD models used in the annotations.
4. Images. The PASCAL images in the 12 categories.


About this Release
==================
The current release only contains images from PASCAL VOC 2012. The ImageNet part will be released soon.
